---
import Page from '@layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page
  title="Submit an API"
  description="Learn how to submit your free public API to the API Hub directory. Follow our step-by-step guide to contribute."
>
  <div style="max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-1); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">
      Submit Your API
    </h1>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 2rem;">
      API Hub sources all data from the open-source
      <a href="https://github.com/public-apis/public-apis" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">public-apis</a>
      repository on GitHub. To get your API listed, you need to contribute directly to that project.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-1); margin: 0 0 1rem;">
      How to Submit
    </h2>

    <ol style="padding-left: 1.25rem; margin: 0 0 2rem;">
      <li style="color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <strong style="color: var(--text-1);">Fork the repository</strong><br />
        Go to <a href="https://github.com/public-apis/public-apis" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/public-apis/public-apis</a> and click "Fork".
      </li>
      <li style="color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <strong style="color: var(--text-1);">Edit the README</strong><br />
        Find the appropriate category section and add your API entry in alphabetical order within its category.
      </li>
      <li style="color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <strong style="color: var(--text-1);">Follow the format</strong><br />
        Each entry must include: API name with link, description, auth type, HTTPS support, and CORS support.
      </li>
      <li style="color: var(--text-2); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        <strong style="color: var(--text-1);">Submit a Pull Request</strong><br />
        Create a PR with a clear title describing your addition. The maintainers will review it.
      </li>
    </ol>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-1); margin: 0 0 1rem;">
      Entry Format
    </h2>
    <div
      style="
        background: var(--surface);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: var(--r-lg);
        padding: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        overflow-x: auto;
      "
    >
      <code style="font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--text-2); white-space: pre;">| [API Name](https://api-url.com) | Short description | `apiKey` | Yes | Yes |</code>
    </div>

    <h3 style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-1); margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">
      Column Reference
    </h3>
    <div style="border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--r-lg); overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.875rem;">
        <thead>
          <tr style="background: var(--surface);">
            <th style="padding: 0.625rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-2); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">Column</th>
            <th style="padding: 0.625rem 1rem; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-2); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">Values</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
            <td style="padding: 0.625rem 1rem; color: var(--text-1); font-weight: 500;">Auth</td>
            <td style="padding: 0.625rem 1rem; color: var(--text-3);"><code style="font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;">apiKey</code>, <code style="font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;">OAuth</code>, <code style="font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;">X-Mashape-Key</code>, or empty</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
            <td style="padding: 0.625rem 1rem; color: var(--text-1); font-weight: 500;">HTTPS</td>
            <td style="padding: 0.625rem 1rem; color: var(--text-3);"><code style="font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;">Yes</code> or <code style="font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;">No</code></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 0.625rem 1rem; color: var(--text-1); font-weight: 500;">CORS</td>
            <td style="padding: 0.625rem 1rem; color: var(--text-3);"><code style="font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;">Yes</code>, <code style="font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;">No</code>, or <code style="font-family: 'Geist Mono', monospace;">Unknown</code></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/public-apis/public-apis/issues/new"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        style="
          display: inline-flex;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 0.5rem;
          padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
          background: var(--accent);
          color: white;
          border-radius: var(--r-md);
          font-weight: 600;
          font-size: 0.9375rem;
          text-decoration: none;
        "
      >
        Submit on GitHub
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Page>
